{"type":null,"faqId":17893,"title":"手机屏幕亮度异常","answer":"<span style=\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21.25pt; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Wingdings; position: relative; top: -1pt;\">l<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21.25pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">请确认光感应器是否正常。光感应器被异物遮挡可能引起屏幕亮度异常。</span><br>\n<span style=\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21.25pt; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Wingdings; position: relative; top: -1pt;\">l<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21.25pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">如果感觉屏幕偏亮或偏暗，请调节屏幕亮度。在<b>设置</b>中的<b>全部设置</b>页签下，点击<b>显示</b>&gt;<b>亮度</b>，拖动滑块调节屏幕亮度。</span><br>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 10.5pt; letter-spacing: -0.2pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: 0cm;\">图1-1</span></div>\n<img border=\"0\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150104110142737001.png\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; width: 393.75pt; height: 217.5pt;\"><br>\n<span style=\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21.25pt; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Wingdings; position: relative; top: -1pt;\">l<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21.25pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">请确认是否进入超级省电模式。超级省电模式下，屏幕会变暗，且只能使用电话、信息和联系人功能。点击“退出”即可退出超级省电模式。</span><br>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 10.5pt; letter-spacing: -0.2pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: 0cm;\">图1-2</span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150104110142724002.png\" align=\"center\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; width: 393.75pt; height: 218.25pt;\"></div>\n<span style=\"line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21.25pt; font-size: 8pt; font-family: Wingdings; position: relative; top: -1pt;\">l<span style=\"font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21.25pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">如果屏幕曾受到外部冲击，内部液晶可能会破损并导致屏幕亮度或色彩异常。请联系客服或携带购机发票前往服务网点检修。</span>\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: 21pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">* </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: 21pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">图示仅供参考，具体操作请以实际手机界面为准。</span>\n<p>\n<br>\n</p>\n</div>","faqTypeId":134,"faqType":"硬件与外观","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"634","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Hardware-Appearance","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1420340578000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":61,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}